er_amount: u64,\n    won_amount: u64,\n    is_winner: bool,\n) -> Result<()>\n```\n\n**Logic**: Increments `total_games`, `total_wagered`; if winner, increments `wins` and `total_won`.\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Platform Program's `lib.rs`**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/platform/src/lib.rs`\n\n**Full Content**: (Lines 1-31)\n\nShows the program declares three instructions:\n- `initialize_platform(treasury: Pubkey)`\n- `create_player_profile()`\n- `update_player_profile(wager_amount, won_amount, is_winner)`\n\nProgram ID: `dYJcBccf1M7yDePcgmiytiEtwr7n4fAaLQAhVPNHgVM`\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Platform Program Instructions Module Structure**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/platform/src/instructions/mod.rs`\n\n**Full Content**: (Lines 1-8)\n\nExports:\n- `create_player_profile` module\n- `initialize_platform` module\n- `update_player_profile` module\n\nAll re-exported for CPI consumption.\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Shared Crate Module Structure**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/src/lib.rs`\n\n**Full Content**: (Lines 1-9)\n\nCurrent modules:\n```rust\npub mod commit_reveal;\npub mod constants;\npub mod escrow;\npub mod fees;\npub mod lifecycle;\npub mod pause;\npub mod tiers;\npub mod timeout;\n```\n\nNo explicit re-exports — just module declarations.\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Shared Crate Dependencies**\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/Cargo.toml`\n\n**Full Content**: (Lines 1-9)\n\nDependencies:\n```toml\n[dependencies]\nanchor-lang = { workspace = true }\nsolana-sha256-hasher = { workspace = true }\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Additional Files Read**\n\n**Platform State Definitions** (`src/state.rs`):\n- `PlatformConfig`: Singleton PDA with authority, treasury, fee_bps, bump\n  - Seeds: `[b\"platform_config\"]`\n- `PlayerProfile`: Per-wallet stats PDA\n  - Seeds: `[b\"player_profile\", wallet.as_ref()]`\n  - Fields: authority, total_games, wins, total_wagered, total_won, bump\n\n**Platform Error Handling** (`src/error.rs`):\n- Single error code: `Unauthorized = 100` (becomes 6100 with #[error_code] offset)\n\n**Platform Initialize** (`initialize_platform.rs`):\n- Creates singleton config PDA\n- Sets treasury and fee_bps from `TOTAL_FEE_BPS` (300 bps from shared)\n\n**Create Player Profile** (`create_player_profile.rs`):\n- Creates player profile PDA for a wallet\n- Initializes all stats to 0\n\n**Coinflip Cargo Dependencies**:\n```toml\nplatform = { path = \"../platform\", features = [\"cpi\"] }\n```\n— Coinflip depends on platform with `cpi` feature enabled\n\n**Fee Constants** (`shared/src/fees.rs`):\n```rust\nTOTAL_FEE_BPS: 300\nREVENUE_BPS: 200\nRAKEBACK_BPS: 70\nCHEST_BPS: 30\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary: CPI Pattern\n\n1. **Caller**: Coinflip program (via config PDA signer)\n2. **Target**: Platform program's `update_player_profile` instruction\n3. **Accounts passed**:\n   - `caller`: Coinflip config PDA (acts as signer)\n   - `profile`: Player's profile PDA (mutable)\n4. **Arguments**:\n   - `wager_amount: u64` — lamports wagered in the game\n   - `won_amount: u64` — lamports won (0 if lost)\n   - `is_winner: bool` — whether player won\n5. **Safety**: Profiles are checked for existence before CPI (skip if empty)\n6. **Result**: Profile stats updated atomically within transaction"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a9931a784404e4f1b (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 40416\ntool_uses: 20\nduration_ms: 44039</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c02d31dc-7289-45e7-92f4-faacb953998d","uuid":"8ebb12a3-6bf0-4b67-b179-5f5107b7019d","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need to understand the CPI pattern for updating player profiles. Find and read these files:\n\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/src/instructions/claim_payout.rs` — look for any CPI call to platform program for updating player profiles\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/so